<br>
This is also why Quick Summoning 3 (50% summoning haste) negates the need for Summoning Haste items, because they can't go above 50%.<br>
<br>
Therefor, the max crit ever possible is:<br>
(2000 * 1.50) + 2000 = <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>5000</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> at level 65 at max focus cap.<br>
